Notes:  [fn2 attached to the italicised names] 2. <i>Kauri</i>, etc. (<i>Kow-ree</i>, To[acute]-ta-ra, Ree[e acute]-moo, <i>Mah[a acute]-ti,</i> Mi-reh, Rah[a acute]-tah, Po-hoo-too-kah[a acute]-wah, <i>Mah[a acute]-noo-kah</i>): New Zealand Bush trees.

